const ArrowRightIcon = () => (
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="16"
    height="16"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    stroke="currentColor"
    strokeWidth="2"
    strokeLinecap="round"
    strokeLinejoin="round"
    className="button-icon"
  >
    <path d="M5 12h14"></path>
    <path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"></path>
  </svg>
)

export default ArrowRightIcon
